oneplus1000:
please give more information about  "this code disable editor drop text". 
because without this code, on Linux I can not drop text file ( to open ). 
I love this app very much that why i want to solve this problem. please.... :-)
**On my machine ( Linux Mint 17 ). When drop file into LiteEditorWidget and I not setAcceptDrops(...) to false MainWindow::dropEvent(QDropEvent event)  will not called.
For this problem I had found two solution.
1) setAcceptDrops(...) to false
or
2)  Implement dragEnterEvent on LiteEditorWidget like this.
void LiteEditorWidget::dragEnterEvent(QDragEnterEvent *event){
    if (event->mimeData()->hasUrls()) {
        event->ignore();
        return;
    }
    QPlainTextEdit::dragEnterEvent(event);
}
